  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together flour and sugar.",
    "Add melted butter and stir until mixture forms a crumbly dough.",
    "Press dough into a 9-inch tart pan with a removable bottom.",
    "Bake for 20-25 minutes or until lightly browned.",
    "In a separate bowl, whisk together maple syrup, eggs, and vanilla extract.",
    "Pour filling into baked tart shell.",
    "Bake for an additional 25-30 minutes or until filling is set.",
    "Top with chopped pecans and bake for 5-10 minutes or until toasted.",
    "Let cool completely before serving."
